---
// 产品详情页
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import BuyButton from "../components/BuyButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="产品详情"
  description="伴旅宝自加热控温杯 BXB-400 产品详情——食品级加热包速热、PP食品级材质、300ml容量、45~55°C暖胃控温。技术参数与产品图集。"
>
  <div class="container-main section">

    <!-- ===== 产品图 + 核心参数 ===== -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- 产品图区域 -->
      <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="text-warm-400 text-lg">🖼️ 产品主图</span>
      </div>

      <!-- 核心参数 -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-warm-900">伴旅宝 自加热控温杯</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-brand-600 font-medium text-lg">型号 BXB-400 · 300ml</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-warm-600">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>型号：BXB-400</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>容量：300ml</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>加热方式：食品级加热包，遇水速热，无需插电</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>控温区间：45~55°C（暖胃适宜温度）</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>杯身材质：PP丙烯与乙烯聚合物（杯盖/内胆/外杯体）</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>密封胶圈：食品级硅橡胶</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>杯套：硅胶（防滑防烫）</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>产品尺寸：高18cm × 直径7.5cm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>产品净重：280g（不含加热包）</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <BuyButton text="查看购买渠道" size="lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 技术参数完整表 ===== -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-6">技术参数</h2>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-warm-200">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <tbody>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700 w-1/3">产品名称</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">伴旅宝自加热控温杯</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">产品型号</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">BXB-400</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">额定容量</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">300ml</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">加热方式</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">食品级专用加热包（遇水反应放热）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">控温区间</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">45~55°C（暖胃适宜温度）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">产品尺寸</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">高 180mm × 直径 75mm</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">产品净重</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">280g（不含加热包）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">杯身材质</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">PP丙烯与乙烯聚合物（杯盖 / 内胆 / 外杯体）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">密封胶圈</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">食品级硅橡胶</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">杯套</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">硅胶（防滑防烫）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">加热包成分</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">铝粉、氧化钙、碳酸钠、碳酸氢钠、活性炭等（食品级）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">适用场景</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-3 text-warm-600">户外出行 / 办公 / 差旅 / 日常暖饮</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 产品演示视频 ===== -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-6">🎬 产品演示</h2>
      <div class="aspect-video bg-warm-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center text-warm-400">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-3">▶️</div>
          <p class="text-lg">产品演示视频</p>
          <p class="text-sm mt-1">展示加热包使用方法与加热效果</p>
          <p class="text-xs mt-3 text-warm-400">（拍摄完成后嵌入视频链接）</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 产品图集 ===== -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-6">产品图集</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">白底主图</div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">场景：通勤</div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">场景：户外</div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">细节：加热仓</div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">细节：杯盖密封</div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 text-sm">包装展示</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 竞品对比表 ===== -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-2">与常见方案对比</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-warm-500 mb-6">一张表看清伴旅宝的优势</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl border border-warm-200">
        <table class="w-full text-sm min-w-[600px]">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-warm-800 text-white text-xs">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium">对比维度</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-medium bg-brand-600">🏷️ 伴旅宝</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-medium">传统保温杯</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-medium">电热杯</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-medium">烧水壶</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-warm-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">加热方式</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">加热包 · 无需电源</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">❌ 不能加热（仅保温）</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">🔌 需要充电</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">🔌 需要插座</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-warm-200 bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">使用场景</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">全场景 · 无限制</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">有热水的地方</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">需提前充电</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">固定场所</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-warm-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">加热温度</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">45~55°C · 暖胃适宜</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">逐渐变凉</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">多档可调（但耗电）</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">沸腾（需等待冷却）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-warm-200 bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">重量/便携性</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">280g · 轻松携带</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">较轻</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">较重（含电池）</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">不可携带</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-warm-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">耗材成本</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">加热包 · 约X元/次</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">无</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">充电电费（极低）</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">电费（极低）</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-warm-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-warm-700">适用饮品</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 font-medium">水/茶/咖啡/牛奶/奶粉</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">需预装热水</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">水/茶/咖啡（清洗麻烦）</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-warm-500">水为主</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-warm-400">
        ※ 耗材成本待确定加热包零售价后填入。电热杯/保温杯数据为市场常见产品参考值。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 加热包成分透明化 ===== -->
    <div class="mt-20 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-warm-50 border border-warm-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">🔬 加热包成分全公开</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        我们选择公开全部成分，因为安全不应该有秘密。以下为伴旅宝食品级专用加热包的全部成分：
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">铝粉</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">还原剂 · 提供热源</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">氧化钙</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">与水反应放热</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">碳酸钠</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">反应促进剂</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">碳酸氢钠</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">pH缓冲 · 安全稳定</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">活性炭</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">吸附 · 净化</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-brand-600">食品级配方</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-1">全成分通过食品安全检测</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
